ide Ohira<ref name=GRG-B-2015 />\n| 15 September 1880\n| 9 May 1995\n| {{ayd | 15 September 1880 | 9 May 1995}}\n| Japan\n\n|-\n| 64\n| data-sort-value=\"Cobb\" | Blanche Cobb<ref name=\"BCobb\">{{cite web | url=http://www.firstcoastnews.com/story/news/local/2014/09/05/jax-woman-turns-114/15140885/ | archive-url=https://archive.today/20140911092737/http://www.firstcoastnews.com/story/news/local/2014/09/05/jax-woman-turns-114/15140885/ | url-status=dead | archive-date=11 September 2014 | title=Jacksonville woman turns 114 Monday | publisher=[[Firstcoastnews.com|First Coast News]] | date=5 September 2014 | accessdate=5 January 2015 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.legacy.com/obituaries/timesunion/obituary.aspx?n=blanche-cobb&pid=174778031&fhid=29355 | title=BLANCHE COBB | date=4 May 2015 | accessdate=4 May 2015}}</ref>\n| 8 September 1900\n| 1 May 2015\n| {{ayd | 8 September 1900 | 1 May 2015}}\n| United States\n\n|-\n| 65\n| data-sort-value=\"Lang\" | Ethel Lang<ref name=GRG-Rankings />\n| 27 May 1900\n| 15 January 2015\n| {{ayd | 27 May 1900 | 15 January 2015}}\n| United Kingdom\n\n|- style=\"background:#9f9;\"\n| style=\"background:#f9f9f9;\"| 66\n| data-sort-value=\"Ford\" | Hester Ford<ref name=GRG-Rankings />\n| 15 August 1905\n| Living\n| {{ayd | 15 August 1905}}\n| United States\n\n|-\n| 67\n| data-sort-value=\"Minagawa\" | Yone Minagawa<ref name=\"YMinagawa\">{{cite web | url= https://www.latimes.com/local/la-me-minagawa14aug14-story.html | title= Yone Minagawa, 114; world\u2019s oldest living person| work=[[Los Angeles Times]] | date=14 August 2007 | accessdate=5 January 2015}}</ref>\n| 4 January 1893\n| 13 August 2007\n| {{ayd | 4 January 1893 | 13 August 2007}}\n| Japan\n\n|-\n| 68\n| data-sort-value=\"Castro\" | Mar\u00eda Antonia Castro<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.demogr.mpg.de/books/drm/007/2-7.pdf|title=International Database on Longevity: Spaniard cases}}</ref>\n| 10 June 1881\n| 16 January 1996\n| {{ayd | 10 June 1881 | 16 January 1996}}\n|