news.net/?p=72685|title=Arguments in Armenia over new banknote design|date=2017-11-27|work=JAMnews|access-date=2018-01-12|language=en-US}}</ref> All denominations for this series are the same as its previous issues, with the 2,000 dram banknote as a newly introduced denomination, the 50,000 dram banknote re-issued for this series and the omission of the 100,000 dram banknote for this issue. The first three denominations, 10,000 {{Armenian dram}}, 20,000 {{Armenian dram}} and 50,000 {{Armenian dram}}, were issued on November 22, 2018. The final three denominations, 1,000 {{Armenian dram}}, 2,000 {{Armenian dram}} and 5,000 {{Armenian dram}} were issued on December 25, 2018. \n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 90%\"\n!colspan=\"9\"|Third series (2018\u2013present)\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"| Image !!rowspan=\"2\"| Value !!rowspan=\"2\"| Dimensions !!rowspan=\"2\"| Main Color !!colspan=\"2\"| Description\n|-\n! Obverse !! Reverse !! Obverse !! Reverse\n|-\n| [[Image:500 Armenian dram - 2017 (obverse).png|300px]]\n| [[Image:500 Armenian dram - 2017 (reverse).png.png|300px]]\n| 500 {{Armenian dram}}\n| 140 \u00d7 76&nbsp;mm\n| Brown and grey\n| [[Noah's Ark]], [[Etchmiadzin Cathedral]] on the background of [[Mount Ararat]]\n| [[Noah]], his family members and animals on the background of [[Mount Ararat]]\n|-\n| [[File:1000 dram 2018 Obverse.jpg|300px|]]  \n| [[File:1000 dram 2018 Reverse.jpg|300px|]]\n| 1,000 {{Armenian dram}}\n| \n| Violet\n| [[Paruyr Sevak]], poems\n| Paryur Sevak house (museum), Zangakatun; statue of Sevak \n|-\n| [[File:2000 dram 2018 Obverse.jpg|300px|]]\n| [[File:2000 dram 2018 Reverse.jpg|300px|]]\n| 2,000 {{Armenian dram}}\n| \n| Brown\n| [[Tigran Petrosian]], chessboard\n| Tigran Petrosyan Chess House (Yerevan), statue of Petrosyan\n|-\n| [[File:5000 dram 2018 Obverse.jpg|300px|]]\n| [[File:5000 dram 2018 Reverse.jpg|300px|]]\n| 5,000 {{Armenian dram}}\n| \n| Red\n| [[William Saroyan]], covers from Saroyan's books, mountain\n| Statue of Saroyan (