untries/Armenia.php Coin Types from Armenia] Lists, pictures, and values of Armenian coin types\n* {{CISCoins|Armenia}}\n* [http://www.bis-ans-ende-der-welt.net/Armenien-B-En.htm The banknotes of Armenia] {{in lang|en|de}}\n\n{{Currencies of Asia}}\n{{Currencies of Europe}}\n{{Currencies of post-Soviet states}}\n{{Armenia topics}}\n\n[[Category:Economy of Armenia]]\n[[Category:Currencies introduced in 1993]]\n", "name_user": "Feltpatpat5", "label": "safe", "comment": "Added Content", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Armenian_dram"}
